Products Registration

Levin’s Pharmadeals International Ltd provide whole assistance cum documents prescribed by regulatory authority of your country and also bear part liabilities /expenses pertaining to it.

We do close follow-up with DRA teams of manufacturers and provide final documents and files (dossiers) as per drug registration guidelines of that country.

LPIL ensures that the process of communication get completed till product registration is not achieved successfully in your country and any deficits or enquiries of regulators are fully attended until objections are over on drug registration applications.

Levins provides-

  • Dossiers (As per the formats of your country – CTD, e-CTD,A-CTD, Hard copy dossier)-Free of cost
  • Dossiers would include all licenses, certificates of manufacturer, D.M.F & S.M.F, stability studies and other information as prescribed in D.R guidelines.
  • Bio-equivalence studies, if required.
  • Samples as per requirement of guidelines.
  • Organize manufacturing site visit of regulators of your country.
